    Combat Probe v1.0 — Anime Squadron combat data discovery
    ------------------------------------------------------------------
    Run this IN A STAGE (not lobby) while your units are fighting.
    It sniffs remotes, workspace models, leaderstats, required modules,
    and (if your executor supports it) getgc() for server combat tables.

    Output: CombatProbe_log.txt in your executor workspace folder.

    getgenv().CombatProbeVerbose = true   -- print every hit to console too
    getgenv().CombatProbeMaxLines = 8000  -- cap log size per session
]]

